     C                   ELSE                                                                       
     C                   MOVEL     '20'          ZXDATD                                             
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
      *                                                                                             
     C                   Z-ADD     @PDATH        ZXDATH                                             
     C     ZXDATH        IFEQ      0                                                                
     C                   Z-ADD     UDATE         ZXDATH                                             
