     C                   SUB       NXCANR        ZXCANT                                             
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
     C                   IF        ZXCANT<=0                                                        
     C                   Z-ADD     0             ZXCANT                                             
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
     C                   IF        NWMAOR=@PMAGA AND NWMADE=@PMAGA                                  
     C                   Z-ADD     0             ZXCANT                                             
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
     C                   IF        NWMADE=@PMAGA                                                    
     C                   Z-SUB     ZXCANT        ZXCANT                                             
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
     C                   IF        M5UNIM<>NXUNIM                                                   
