      **************************************************************                                
      * SUBRUTINA PARA CONVERTIR UNIDADES PEDIDO A UNIDADES STOCK  *                                
      **************************************************************                                
     C     CS_CNVUBS     BEGSR                                                                      
     C                   EVAL      XZAUXI=ZXAUXIBS                                                  
     C                   MOVE      ZXARTIBS      P6ARTI                                             
     C                   MOVE      ZXVARIBS      P6VARI                                             
     C                   MOVE      ZXMODEBS      P6MODE                                             
     C                   MOVE      ZXUNIMBS      P6UNIM                                             
     C                   MOVE      '0'           P6TCOF                                             
     C                   Z-ADD     0             P6COFA                                             
     C     KPMUNAL       CHAIN     PMUNAL                             81                            
     C                   IF        *IN81=*ON                                                        
     C                   EVAL      P6VARI=*BLANKS                                                   
     C                   EVAL      P6MODE=*BLANKS                                                   
     C     KPMUNAL       CHAIN     PMUNAL                             81                            
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
     C                   IF        P6TCOF<>'1'                                                      
     C                   MULT      P6COFA        XZAUXI                                             
     C                   ELSE                                                                       
     C                   IF        P6COFA<>0                                                        
     C                   DIV       P6COFA        XZAUXI                                             
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
     C                   MOVE      '0'           XZDECI                                             
     C                   MOVE      '0'           XZAJUD                                             
