15070C     KMSALDD07     SETLL     MSALDD05                                                         
     C                   DO        *HIVAL                                                           
15070C*    KMSALDD07     READE     MSALDD07                               88                        
15070C     KMSALDD07     READE     MSALDD05                               88                        
     C   88              LEAVE                                                                      
